OL,3,CTaoiseach hopes for further 'progress'
OL,4,Con tax rate bands in budget
OL,6,FSimon Harris has expressed confidence
OL,7,Fthat the Government will be able to
OL,8,Fmake further progress increasing the
OL,9,Fhigher tax band threshold in the
OL,10,Fbudget.
OL,12,FAt the Fine Gael ard fheis in April,
OL,13,FMr Harris restated an ambition to
OL,14,Fraise the threshold to 50,000 euro and
OL,15,Fpromised to further reduce the
OL,16,FUniversal Social Charge (USC) burden
OL,17,Fon low and middle-income earners.
