OL,3,CTaoiseach hopes for further 'progress'
OL,4,Con tax rate bands in budget
OL,6,FHe subsequently made clear that
OL,7,Fincreasing the current top tax rate
OL,8,Ffrom the current threshold of 42,000
OL,9,Feuro to 50,000 euro would not be
OL,10,Fachieved in a single budget.
OL,12,FIn his latest comments on the
OL,13,Fpotential shape of October's budget,
OL,14,Fthe Taoiseach said he hoped the
OL,15,FGovernment could make further progress
OL,16,Fon increasing tax thresholds.
OL,18,FThe Fine Gael leader suggested more
OL,19,Fcuts to USC rates and moves on
OL,20,Finheritance tax would also be under
OL,21,Fconsideration.
