OL,3,CTaoiseach hopes for further 'progress'
OL,4,Con tax rate bands in budget
OL,6,F"We have indications in the Summer
OL,7,FEconomic Statement that we'd have
OL,8,Faround 1.4 billion euro available for
OL,9,Ftax measures, that's pretty much the
OL,10,Fexact same as we had last year, so
OL,11,Fthat gives you an indication of the
OL,12,Fscale of options that are available to
OL,13,Fgovernment," he said.
