OL,3,CTaoiseach hopes for further 'progress'
OL,4,Con tax rate bands in budget
OL,6,F"It is important to me that you don't
OL,7,Fhave a situation where somebody's
OL,8,Fwages go up, or somebody does a few
OL,9,Fhours of overtime, or you know gets a
OL,10,Fpromotion, that all of a sudden they
OL,11,Ffind the state clawing back more and
OL,12,Fmore of their money. That's a
OL,13,Fdisincentive to the very principle of
OL,14,Fmaking work pay.
OL,16,F"We've consistently made progress on
OL,17,Fincreasing those income bands. I'd
OL,18,Fhope we could do that again.
