OL,3,CTaoiseach hopes for further 'progress'
OL,4,Con tax rate bands in budget
OL,6,F"I also said at the ard fheis that
OL,7,Flater this year my party would also
OL,8,Foutline, from a party point of view,
OL,9,Four own tax strategy for the next five
OL,10,Fyears and I think that's important as
OL,11,Fwell that people know the direction of
OL,12,Ftravel that I and my party would like
OL,13,Fto see taxation policy go in the years
OL,14,Fahead."
OL,16,FThe forthcoming budget will be worth
OL,17,F8.3 billion euro, comprising a
OL,18,Fspending package of 6.9 billion euro
OL,19,Fand a tax package worth 1.4 billion
OL,20,Feuro.
